history.content:
Girls Teaching Girls to Code is excited to announce our Virtual Career Panel event!

If you’re female-identifying and interested in learning more about careers in COMPUTER SCIENCE and TECH, come come come to our virtual event this weekend!!!!

The career panel is a two-part webinar featuring stories of women in the tech industry. Part one will focus on how computer science can be applied to multiple industries, while part two will focus on exploring the different roles in tech. This semester, we will be featuring women working as UI/UX Designers, Product Managers, Software Engineers, and women working in social good, government and policy, healthcare, and more!

JOIN US HERE: bit.ly/2020gtcpanel

Here’s FB event link: https://fb.me/e/D6IqCUwh
